"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Lateral view of wrist",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 346px; height: 504px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    This lateral radiograph of a normal adult wrist shows the outlines of scaphoid, lunate, and capitate bones.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
